                        "name": "admwiggin",
                        "displayName": "Tianon Gravi",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This is a *one line* fix.  All that needs to be done is add \"$request->getBaseUrl()\" to the return of the simple() function, as per the patch code.\n\n30 Minutes is *too long* of an estimate.  Why isn't this fixed yet?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
