                        "name": "stevecrozz",
                        "displayName": "Stephen Crosby",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "@Tianon , I agree, but it seems like Matthew hasn't had the time to do it yet. I've asked about it on the IRC channel and I've been told I should bring it up on the mailing list, but I haven't yet. You could probably speed it up by asking around on the mailing list.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=stevecrozz",
                        "name": "stevecrozz",
                        "displayName": "Stephen Crosby",
